ssets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過我老母仲煩 一逆佢意就發哂癲咁 有時唔係唔想反抗而係有其他原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家已經好過以前 中學個陣門禁係8點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好在我唔係幾鐘意去夜街 又無咩朋友 所以都唔會比老母屌我夜番<br />\n有時同男朋友出去過夜會有說話聽下咁<br />\n而家最管得嚴就係唔比閂房門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話閂左門就唔知我係入面做咩 有次好唔開心想自己冷靜下 哩埋自己係被竇入面喊 佢竟然拉開張被係咁問咩事咩事 真係少少私隱都唔比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6bb91bec2810b103e146d2242ac0c8e995358a","tid":2163742,"uid":224285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feef5f9207cd2b8d9f00d99a30c3e3d973b7e93a","tid":2163742,"uid":65346,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T00:24:54.000Z","msg":"有時 d  父母真係管好死<br />\n到有一日你搬走,又話你衰..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人生好難"},{"pid":"61d662a1902d4adc0ec6d06ae1573180d1da3b27","tid":2163742,"uid":271545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個嬲嬲表情幾得意"},{"pid":"a50cf7482e9ce3bb1a2a778d777dca9a652e9dfa","tid":2163742,"uid":242723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:41:35.000Z","msg":"其實話熄電話就得個啲係咪啲阿媽唔打人<br />\n利申：廿頭 唔夠阿媽打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3c50ecd7ca55a60114d72dda32399408f9dc02","tid":2163742,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c5a4bcebc377b1b40790a736ca644dad6725474","tid":2163742,"uid":224285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55c4a2a8d447ca6d25b6d684d89fe8bf9e1cc6a9","tid":2163742,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4751a01ca87c65b137c8ac02a589d8a5d68197d","tid":2163742,"uid":15